cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with video captioning, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves attention mechanisms, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper evaluates its approach on benchmark datasets, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
